538
00:32:11,310 --> 00:32:11,900
No!

539
00:32:13,840 --> 00:32:15,120
I beg you, Shanggu!

540
00:32:16,600 --> 00:32:17,910
This is my responsibility
as the Chief God.

541
00:32:19,550 --> 00:32:21,080
I have to protect the world.

542
00:32:40,240 --> 00:32:40,840
Bai Jue.

543
00:32:41,200 --> 00:32:42,030
Don’t worry.

544
00:32:42,480 --> 00:32:44,030
I will be a qualified Chief God

545
00:32:44,360 --> 00:32:45,760
