to the God Realm.

546
00:34:59,150 --> 00:34:59,910
Master!

547
00:36:09,390 --> 00:36:10,040
Master!

548
00:36:10,670 --> 00:36:11,350
Shanggu!

549
00:36:14,720 --> 00:36:15,630
Master Bai Jue!

550
00:36:29,320 --> 00:36:29,870
Bai Jue.

