No way!

554
00:36:39,480 --> 00:36:40,350
Destruction Pestle?!

555
00:36:46,390 --> 00:36:47,670
How dare you collude with the Devils!

556
00:36:48,110 --> 00:36:49,110
I’ll settle accounts with you later!

557
00:36:51,590 --> 00:36:52,200
Master!

558
00:37:23,350 --> 00:37:23,870
Shanggu.

559
00:37:24,830 --> 00:37:25,460
Don’t!

560
00:37:25,630 --> 00:37:26,220
Bai Jue.

561
00:37:27,320 --> 00:37:28,000
Just go.

562
00:37:29,520 --> 00:37:32,040
I don’t want to look at you

563
00:37:33,280 --> 00:37:34,670
die for my own fate innocently

564
00:37:36,870 --> 00:37:38,040
one by one.

565
00:37:39,070 --> 00:37:39,720
I know.

566
00:37:40,760 --> 00:37:41,670
I know it better than anyone.

567
00:37:43,280 --> 00:37:44,800
You can be responsible
for the lives of common people,

568
00:37:45,280 --> 00:37:46,070
and you’re able to take the responsibility
of being the Chief God.

569
00:37:49,150 --> 00:37:50,870
I have never made any mistake
in my life.

570
00:37:53,320 --> 00:37:54,350
I regret only one thing

571
00:37:55,670 --> 00:37:56,630
so far.

572
00:37:58,040 --> 00:37:59,590
It was me who forced you
to become the Chief God.

573
00:38:01,480 --> 00:38:02,320
I pushed you

574
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:03,670
into this perdition.

575
00:38:03,900 --> 00:38:08,800
♪Ten thousand years of ups and downs
are just in a moment♪

576
00:38:08,800 --> 00:38:11,070
Actually, I just want to ask you if

577
00:38:13,070 --> 00:38:14,320
that mountain of pears

578
00:38:15,350 --> 00:38:16,590
and the sky full of stars

579
00:38:19,280 --> 00:38:20,560
you gave me yesterday

580
00:38:21,590 --> 00:38:22,520
are true?

581
00:38:24,760 --> 00:38:25,590
I gave them to you with my whole heart.

582
00:38:32,870 --> 00:38:33,830
You also said that

583
00:38:35,320 --> 00:38:36,280
you wanted to listen to music with me,

584
00:38:36,590 --> 00:38:37,280
read books with me,

585
00:38:38,070 --> 00:38:38,960
ride horse with me,

586
00:38:39,590 --> 00:38:40,520
and be with me day by day

587
00:38:41,320 --> 00:38:42,280
forever.

588
00:38:43,150 --> 00:38:43,870
Did you lie to me?

589
00:38:45,200 --> 00:38:46,040
They are all true.

590
00:38:46,560 --> 00:38:47,280
Come back now.

591
00:38:48,760 --> 00:38:50,320
It would be all good
if I was born a few years earlier.

592
00:38:51,800 --> 00:38:53,070
If I met you 70,000 years ago,

593
00:38:54,040 --> 00:38:55,110
grew up with you,

594
00:38:57,480 --> 00:38:58,200
then

595
00:38:58,760 --> 00:39:00,070
we would have 70,000 years

596
00:39:00,200 --> 00:39:00,910
get along with each other.

597
00:39:03,830 --> 00:39:04,480
I…

598
00:39:04,480 --> 00:39:07,020
♪Perseverance♪

599
00:39:08,110 --> 00:39:08,960
Unfortunately,

600
00:39:10,280 --> 00:39:11,280
God’s life is too long.

601
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:12,910
I never cherished it.

602
00:39:14,430 --> 00:39:15,390
Don’t…

603
00:39:18,830 --> 00:39:19,670
The lives of common people
are too important.

604
00:39:20,560 --> 00:39:21,350
I have no choice.

605
00:39:22,520 --> 00:39:23,110
Shanggu.

606
00:39:24,320 --> 00:39:24,870
Shanggu.

607
00:39:25,630 --> 00:39:26,200
Bai Jue.

608
00:39:27,430 --> 00:39:28,070
I’ll leave the Three Realms

609
00:39:31,200 --> 00:39:32,240
to you.

610
00:39:33,110 --> 00:39:33,630
No!

611
00:39:34,760 --> 00:39:35,280
No way!

612
00:39:45,630 --> 00:39:46,150
Shanggu!

613
00:39:48,350 --> 00:39:48,910
Shanggu!

614
00:39:50,110 --> 00:39:50,760
No way!

615
00:39:54,520 --> 00:39:55,520
Shanggu, come back!

616
00:39:56,800 --> 00:39:57,620
I’m begging you!

617
00:39:57,620 --> 00:40:00,300
♪Snow and smoke are in the dusk♪

618
00:40:01,020 --> 00:40:05,580
♪Ask for the love of this life♪

619
00:40:18,080 --> 00:40:18,830
Shanggu!

620
00:40:28,460 --> 00:40:29,390
Shanggu!

621
00:40:30,900 --> 00:40:35,180
♪She turned into ashes♪

622
00:40:35,740 --> 00:40:37,760
♪Life and death♪

623
00:40:37,760 --> 00:40:38,590
Shanggu.

624
00:40:38,590 --> 00:40:41,800
♪He protects the Three Realms for her♪

625
00:40:41,800 --> 00:40:42,630
I wish I could be with you

626
00:40:44,000 --> 00:40:44,760
not as a god

627
00:40:46,630 --> 00:40:47,760
in the next life.

628
00:40:48,660 --> 00:40:51,220
♪Repeat it again♪

629
00:40:51,540 --> 00:40:56,900
♪This love is boundless
and never extinguished♪

630
00:41:22,520 --> 00:41:23,630
I won’t let you die!

631
00:41:48,760 --> 00:41:54,160
♪Year after year time goes by♪

632
00:41:55,120 --> 00:42:01,160
♪Don’t be afraid Fate comes back♪

633
00:42:01,800 --> 00:42:08,160
♪Rain floods and memories last♪

634
00:42:08,320 --> 00:42:14,480
♪I won’t stop missing you
no matter what♪

635
00:42:14,480 --> 00:42:20,760
♪Years have passed and I keep staying♪

636
00:42:21,280 --> 00:42:27,560
♪I experience endless sadness
but never leave♪

637
00:42:28,020 --> 00:42:34,160
♪Staying away and loving you greatly♪

638
00:42:35,340 --> 00:42:41,520
♪I’d wait through the lifetime♪

639
00:42:52,360 --> 00:42:58,980
♪I spend years waiting
for returned birds♪

640
00:42:58,980 --> 00:43:05,580
♪I never regret
and let no one replace you♪

641
00:43:05,580 --> 00:43:12,500
♪Hope we’ll figure out the past
when we wake up♪

642
00:43:12,940 --> 00:43:20,580
♪I’ll finally confess to you♪

643
00:43:21,420 --> 00:43:27,340
♪Along the way I watch flowers
bloom and wither♪

644
00:43:28,080 --> 00:43:34,880
♪Maybe we part because we’ll meet again♪

645
00:43:34,960 --> 00:43:41,600
♪Tears turn into clouds and rain drops♪

646
00:43:41,640 --> 00:43:48,040
♪When everything works out♪

647
00:43:48,040 --> 00:43:57,340
♪I’ll enjoy a free life with you
for a thousand years♪

